            <div id="lts-overview" class="project-overview">
                <h3 class="overview-name">project overview —</h3>
                <p class="overview">Across: Word Puzzle Kit is a puzzles box targeting adults. Across was designed with
                    the intention of keeping the audience entertained within every inch of the box. Each piece of
                    copywriting or graphic points them to a new mystery. The kit contains a guidebook, pencils and
                    eraser, puzzle cards, and a binder.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="lts-goals" class="project-goals">
                <h3 class="goals-name">goals —</h3>
                <p class="goals">By leaving Easter eggs around the box, the design allows the audience to explore the
                    kit at their own pace to find the hidden compartment while still being able to enjoy the puzzles.
                    Across aims to create a calming yet intriguing environment for its audience and take the frustration
                    out of the process of solving a puzzle.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
